{"ts":"2026-07-18T15:19:21.123Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-18T15:19:21.122Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Implementation evidence 2026-07-18: added public commitWorkspaceTransaction with a durable per-workspace journal, one writer lock, ordered idempotent inspection/application, deterministic replay, reverse append-style compensation, explicit crash interruption semantics, extension-host binding, and public SDK export. pm-vcs merge is the non-PM consumer and binds transaction identity to changeset+ref. Verification: 5,914 tests across 311 files at exact 100/100/100/100 (39,043 statements; 27,456 branches; 7,949 functions; 38,008 lines); lint/zero-clone/static/docstring/package-boundary/token/audit gates clean. Packed temp consumer committed+replayed the SDK transaction and completed VCS ref/create/propose/merge/log plus deep doctor at /tmp/pm-sdk-transaction-proof-P5Bp3l. Release gates passed through packed smoke and 88-command dogfood; only the expected pre-commit Greptile stage remained."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T15:19:21.123Z"}],"before_hash":"61985e0501ff304b8d2a144b13918edd8ac6eb8ec818bd5178a3fac1883369d9","after_hash":"43a573f42855285ae56a0a1dfdc6b753f060e2efe9d2da4de492115611c1dabe"}
{"ts":"2026-07-18T15:36:41.211Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/2","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-18T15:36:41.210Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Pre-push Greptile review b4db10ed-d5b4-4ff0-84b3-ba2ee8f3209a (confidence 3/5, five findings) was fully accepted: result-free apply now has an honest undefined return contract; callers can configure positive lock TTL/wait bounds; the journal is read once per attempt; VCS SDK host access is guarded with a descriptive error; and the compensation race test uses a new semantic step_compensating transition instead of storage-call ordinals. Post-fix full verification: 311 files / 5,914 tests, exact 100/100/100/100 (39,051 statements; 27,460 branches; 7,951 functions; 38,017 lines), typecheck, ESLint, zero clones, static/docstrings, package boundary, and token budget all pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T15:36:41.211Z"}],"before_hash":"43a573f42855285ae56a0a1dfdc6b753f060e2efe9d2da4de492115611c1dabe","after_hash":"f553f6c84c7eed2a0f8b1d10c9fd4111da36b98a98a50015fcc83d18927d6e72"}
